                    <span>This is mother of all books on VB6! Balena is trully amazing in delivering a hands-on coverage of Visual Basic programming. I have read quite a few books on VB6, but this one is my favorite.<BR>If you're planning to do some serious programming, you owe yourself a copy. And if you find it difficult to spend $30 to get one, you can always go to VB2THEMAX.COM for plenty of free code, tips, tricks and all.</span>
                  
